{"layoutParsingResults": [{"prunedResult": {"page_count": null, "width": 2219, "height": 2981, "model_settings": {"use_doc_preprocessor": false, "use_seal_recognition": true, "use_table_recognition": true, "use_formula_recognition": true, "use_chart_recognition": false, "use_region_detection": true, "format_block_content": false, "markdown_ignore_labels": ["number", "footnote", "header", "header_image", "footer", "footer_image", "aside_text"]}, "parsing_res_list": [{"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "大清山神庙香火地碑记", "block_bbox": [287, 260, 767, 308], "block_id": 0, "block_order": 1}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "凡事不记则不明，不记之于石则明不彰，欲求远不休，有必先书之于石，以铭其疆界。则地邻不得侵，小宵不得骗，施主不得悔，然后香火之地得以万世常昭，久而不少矣。刻之于石，良有以也。是为序。\n", "block_bbox": [187, 329, 1271, 646], "block_id": 1, "block_order": 2}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "乙卯科中式候选知县杜含章撰杜廷琏术手拜书", "block_bbox": [288, 668, 901, 783], "block_id": 2, "block_order": 3}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "计开香火地亩：", "block_bbox": [286, 803, 597, 849], "block_id": 3, "block_order": 4}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "旧香火地庙前路东地乙段东至河心西至路南至路北至河心\n", "block_bbox": [190, 870, 1265, 985], "block_id": 4, "block_order": 5}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "路西地乙段东至路西至堰南至路\n庙西地一段东至庙西至堰南至路北至河心至嘉庆三年经管钱粮人王玉俊李振德杜廷梅杜迪义续置口派老房屋口熟地乙分坐", "block_bbox": [191, 1009, 1176, 1256], "block_id": 5, "block_order": 6}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1316, 258, 1834, 1167], "block_id": 6, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "南至口东截古路西截路北至口口截口路西截口□落西圪塔价钱六十八千粮三升三合东至官地西至路嘉庆六年岁次乙丑闰六月吉日功德主王玉俊李良德同立", "block_bbox": [285, 1276, 1415, 1457], "block_id": 7, "block_order": 7}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "明故处士芬园公之墓", "block_bbox": [288, 1542, 714, 1587], "block_id": 8, "block_order": 8}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "公讳芳，字国香，明之嘉靖人也。高祖廪膳生员跃龙公第四子，配范氏，生平勤俭醇谨，克继家声，其卒也，始葬于洼皮岭，后移葬今之茔下。乾隆五十二年，曾孙等乃于此地葬焉。生三子：长槐，初葬于缸窑沟，后迁葬今茔之东北，乾隆五十一年始同葬于茔左；次栓，葬于北大平口口，移葬于南大平。生二女：长适天坛李姓，次适仁村秦姓，孙等恐其久而湮没，故勒石以示后焉。\n", "block_bbox": [183, 1608, 1317, 2141], "block_id": 9, "block_order": 9}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "时嘉庆六年岁次辛酉谷旦", "block_bbox": [283, 2166, 804, 2213], "block_id": 10, "block_order": 10}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "掘井碑记", "block_bbox": [283, 2307, 483, 2352], "block_id": 11, "block_order": 11}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "尝思畴行口行水居其口口口口是以先五行而冠六府□□口口之地中有水谓师师者口口口口合也先王以建万国亲□□□□并□丧无得往来井井之□□□□毕或在东河口泉工，或在南坻坞□口德杜天德等念涸辄之口口列可食男妇老幼莫不□（下缺）\n", "block_bbox": [178, 2373, 1318, 2697], "block_id": 12, "block_order": 12}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1354, 1488, 1825, 2721], "block_id": 13, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "image", "block_content": "", "block_bbox": [1937, 520, 2048, 606], "block_id": 14, "block_order": null}, {"block_label": "paragraph_title", "block_content": "渑池杜氏宗谱", "block_bbox": [1957, 781, 2041, 1538], "block_id": 15, "block_order": 13}, {"block_label": "text", "block_content": "三八二", "block_bbox": [1969, 2251, 2026, 2378], "block_id": 16, "block_order": 14}], "layout_det_res": {"boxes": [{"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9789544939994812, "coordinate": [183.8021240234375, 1608.656005859375, 1317.952392578125, 2141.528076171875]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.9756759405136108, "coordinate": [1316.1912841796875, 258.751220703125, 1834.8341064453125, 1167.1549072265625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9621505737304688, "coordinate": [178.07366943359375, 2373.926025390625, 1318.317626953125, 2697.789306640625]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9568274021148682, "coordinate": [187.69769287109375, 329.366943359375, 1271.015625, 646.741455078125]}, {"cls_id": 2, "label": "text", "score": 0.9122943878173828, "coordinate": [190.3231201171875, 870.583740234375, 1265.54345703125, 985.307373046875]}, {"cls_id": 1, "label": "image", "score": 0.8749746680259705, "coor